                    .inside
                        p Avery Cooper is a multi-instrumentalist, bandleader, and educator in the Burlington area. 
                        p He graduated from UVM in 2017 with a jazz performance degree. 
                        p He is well versed in alto, tenor and baritone sax, flute, as well as music theory and composition. 
                        p Now, he works at Champlain Valley Union and Edmonds Middle School, in addition to taking on private lessons. 
                
